@startuml
title Timing advanced geometry oracle
concise "Request phase" as PHASE
robust BUS
binary "Enable" as EN
clock "Clock" as CLK with period 6 pulse 2 offset 0
@0
PHASE is {Queued}
BUS is {Idle}
EN is off
@+5
PHASE is {Running}
BUS is {Run}
EN is on
@+3 EN is off
@5 <-> @12 : active window
highlight 12 to 18 : cooldown
@18
PHASE is {Done}
BUS is {Wait}
EN is low
@enduml
